      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014spotless inside and out, smoke-free, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping this beauty in tip-top condition, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
      "price": 43900.0,
