    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system, delivering surgical throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example features a fully reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing the chassis's primary lateral stress point\u2014and has undergone a comprehensive rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical integrity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings, while the exterior retains its original depth and luster, free of typical clear-coat degradation or oxidation on the shadowline trim.",
